doi: "10.5281/zenodo.20040430"

keywords:
  - molecular dynamics
  - GROMACS
  - structural biology
  - protein simulation
  - trajectory analysis
  - free energy landscape
  - principal component analysis
  - mixed-solvent MD
  - computational drug discovery
  - Python

